<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>yà bó lā hǎn xìn shén de huà 迦南802</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yè sè chén chén, tiān shàng liàng jīng jīng. yà bó lā hǎn dào mén wài wàng tiān kōng.
 shén duì tā shuō, nǐ de hòu yì yào xiàng tiān shàng de zhòng xīng, shù yě shù bù qīng.
 a a, yà bó lā hǎn xìn shén de huà, shén jiù gěi tā zuò chéng.</lyrics>
</song>